</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1000">2.5. Editing an appointment</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Click on an appointment to open the appointment details and edit the details.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Editing an appointment:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Start » Calendar</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the appointment that you would like to edit.<br>
→ The window <strong>Appointment details</strong> will be displayed.</p>
