<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1100">2.6. Deleting an appointment</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Delete appointments when they have been created by mistake or when they have become obselete.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Deleting an appointment:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Start » Calendar</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the appointment that you would like to delete.<br>
→ The window <strong>Appointment details</strong> will be displayed.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Delete</strong>.<br>
→ The appointment will be deleted and removed from the calendar overview.</p>
</li>
</ol>
